Rem !

240
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:23,770
Rem !

241
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,470
Hyu…

242
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:27,630
ma…

243
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:32,440
Rem, tu…

244
00:19:33,870 --> 00:19:37,030
Vis…

245
00:19:37,660 --> 00:19:40,730
Rem, reste avec moi…

246
