Vis…

247
00:19:51,850 --> 00:19:54,860
Je t’adore…

248
00:19:59,070 --> 00:19:59,960
Rem ?

249
00:20:22,330 --> 00:20:23,740
Allons-y, Rem.

250
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:53,560
Bételgeuse…

251
00:20:57,670 --> 00:20:59,570
Bételgeuse…

252
00:21:21,210 --> 00:21:24,240
Bételgeuse !

253
00:21:27,230 --> 00:21:31,140
Bételgeuse !

254
00:21:38,580 --> 00:21:39,560
Repose à jamais…

255
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:42,280
avec ma chère fille.

